{"datas":[{"id":"1491130588225","title":"老蘭画说嘚啵嘚：在我最没能力的年纪，遇到了最想照顾一生的姑娘","titleImg":"avatar_2/1491130574095.jpg","content":"<p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">有句话叫“无福消受”，说的是已经拥有了，但却没命享受。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">这表面上看挺遗憾，细想，也正常。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">因为“无福消受”的“福”多是来路不正。二是来的过多。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">当年沈阳出过慕马大案，其中的马叫马向东。此人一路官运亨通，但最后却拿着50万美元在澳门豪赌，这种人不出事上帝都不会答应。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">人要学会知足，要的东西要有限。无限度索取，即使索来了也得倒回去。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">这叫无福消受。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br></p><div class=\"image-package\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25px; width: 700px; margin-left: -40px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1996705-03a5305251566c7c.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: zoom-in; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;\"><br><div class=\"image-caption\" style=\"min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; min-height: 22px; display: inline-block; padding: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(217, 217, 217); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7;\">图片发自简书App</div></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">﻿﻿那天在网上看到一句话，说画画的人都有的十种能力!什么感受力、观察力、想象力、忍耐力、记忆力、思维能力、造型能力、审美能力、分析能力、概括能力……说的简直跟个神一样。﻿<br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">有机会做一件能通神的事情，为什么不呢。　﻿</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">更让人血脉偾张还有这样一句话——这辈子一定要找个画画的人结婚。﻿</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">虽然这辈子我已经找到了好老婆。﻿</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">但不是还有下辈子吗？</p><div class=\"image-package\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25px; width: 700px; margin-left: -40px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1996705-383890d381cd489f.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: zoom-in; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;\"><br><div class=\"image-caption\" style=\"min-width: 20%; max-width: 80%; min-height: 22px; display: inline-block; padding: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(217, 217, 217); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); line-height: 1.7;\">图片发自简书App</div></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">﻿﻿还是在网上看到的——在我最无能力的年纪遇见了最想照顾一生的姑娘。刚想感慨两句，一想，拉屁倒吧，就是现在我遇上了，也一样照顾不好人家。还是赶紧努力，把现在身边的女人照顾好吧，扯些没用的干啥。</p><div class=\"image-package\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25px; width: 700px; margin-left: -40px; text-align: center; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1996705-a98505262b42f545.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: zoom-in; transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;\"></div>\n\n        "}]}